  "body": "<p>Every time I get the latest collection samples to work on catalog materials, I get goosebumps. Sometimes I dive right in and make a bunch of projects, while other times I just like to sit and stare at the new product. This time it was a mix of both pleasures. The funny thing is that when I first started putting together this post, I typed the title, \"Amy Tangerine dies\", and that just sounded much too morbid. But really, I did want to introduce <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=plus%20one%20dies&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D65223%2F366860%2Ddie%2Ddies%2Dwafer%2FDetail\">the die set</a> that's new to American Crafts and part of the <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=plus%20one&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2DAmy%2DTangerine%2DPlus%2DOne%2FCategories\">Plus One collection</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599118886637-5ZXBYVZB5UG3RF7RMOY2/6a-DSC_3256-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>It's great not only for card makers, but also scrapbookers and Project Lifers. The polaroid style frame is 3x4 inches and fits perfectly into a PL pocket. The embossed stitched details are my favorite part. And I love the little heart.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599118905534-9IGW4A6S7FQDUVT22994/6b-DSC_3258-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599118918545-3T2IKTFGPTPATK42DLLY/6c-DSC_3259-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Using the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/147243-counterpart-12x12-plus-one-amy-tangerine-paper/\">Counterpart paper</a> as the background, I layered on the goodness. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/146847-plus-one-amy-tangerine-accompany-large-clear-acrylic-stamp/\">\"Darling\"</a> was stamped with <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=mama%20elephant%20ocean&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D63388%2Fmama%2Delephant%2Dme%2Ddsh%2Doce%2Docean%2FDetail\">Mama Elephant ink in my new favorite color, Ocean</a>. I also used the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/147272-plus-one-amy-tangerine-teammate-embroidery-icon-stencil-kit/\">stitching template</a> for the house and made a stitched corner detail using half of the square.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599118935587-91AL37NQEJQN59VLJBSU/6d-DSC_3260-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599118959585-0KNJ9WQKTVSHAR0PZOUZ/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599118968672-X9DSQGW40JN9X1KRJUCK/6f-seriously1-600x592.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For more, shop <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=plus%20one&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2DAmy%2DTangerine%2DPlus%2DOne%2FCategories\">Plus One at Simon Says Stamp</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
